{"tid":1903172,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"2020 DSer 係時候溫翻書啦","createTime":"2020-02-28T19:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T19:12:22.000Z","uid":311034,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1899a09040105c5e214520a2081bc60fed505bf9","tid":1903172,"uid":311034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:39:20.000Z","msg":"坦白講點解要推遲 一直都唔明 推遲幾個禮拜改變到d咩？ 肺炎會突然冇左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解唔趁早考 趁未到高峰期考左先？定你地想高峰期先考？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同我講會影響發揮水平？ 有料嘅點都會識 加上DSE係拉curve 即使會影響狀態 咁最多全港條curve低d 你個grad唔會變架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2020 DSEr 唔好俾咁多藉口自己逃避啦 要求推遲個班 有幾多個真係驚肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係驚你可以推遲一年考 今年個DSE你又冇俾到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 係時候溫翻書啦 唔好將來做黑警呀 加油啦 唔好輸俾支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家溫翻仲泥得切！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d71a60caf51cb507b15a638294abfc3aa96515","tid":1903172,"uid":262880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:40:52.000Z","msg":"溫緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c049a02faca1725cb8d809b736a26e3c2e493ef","tid":1903172,"uid":127770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:41:05.000Z","msg":"2021 一定要得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30aca244557f06fd868ec6d92502063f6033cbf3","tid":1903172,"uid":258220,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T19:43:37.000Z","msg":"本身讀書已經差 而家日日都要擔心出面嘅手足 又有武漢肺炎 都唔知點算 都加上呢排又有感情問題 又大壓力 真係好撚攰 日日都係坐喺度打機睇新聞直播 都唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.g